Class Outcast

  • java.lang.Object
    • Outcast

  • public class Outcast
extends java.lang.Object
    Finds the odd ones out of the provided nouns, The class maintains a WordNet beneath it and uses it to help the client identify the most odd word (called outcast) among a given set.
